---
export interface Props {
  imageSrc?: string;
}

const { imageSrc = "https://www.ominta.ma/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/nettoyage-tanger.jpg" } = Astro.props;
---

<!-- ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════
     WHY CHOOSE US SECTION (split layout)
     Source: post-27581.css — elements 87767da, 8bcd8f1,
     3238387, 401991f, 84d8f7e, 0340331, e690d50
═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════ -->
<section class="why-choose-section">

  <!-- ── Left: Full-bleed image background ─────────── -->
  <div class="why-choose-image" style={`background-image: url('${imageSrc}');`}>
    <!-- Image applied via inline CSS background -->
  </div>

  <!-- ── Right: Green gradient with content ────────── -->
  <div class="why-choose-content">
    <div class="why-choose-inner">

      <h2 class="why-title"> Pourquoi choisir  notre société de nettoyage</h2>

      <div class="why-features"> 

        <!-- Feature 1 -->
        <div class="feature-box">
          <div class="feature-icon">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="36" height="36" viewBox="0 0 512 512" fill="currentColor" aria-hidden="true">
              <!-- FontAwesome fa-search-location (\f689) -->
              <path d="M505 442.7L405.3 343c-4.5-4.5-10.6-7-17-7H372c27.6-35.3 44-79.7 44-128C416 93.1 322.9 0 208 0S0 93.1 0 208s93.1 208 208 208c48.3 0 92.7-16.4 128-44v16.3c0 6.4 2.5 12.5 7 17l99.7 99.7c9.4 9.4 24.6 9.4 33.9 0l28.3-28.3c9.4-9.4 9.4-24.6.1-34zM208 336c-70.7 0-128-57.2-128-128 0-70.7 57.2-128 128-128 70.7 0 128 57.2 128 128 0 70.7-57.2 128-128 128z"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <div class="feature-text">
            <h4 class="feature-title">Intervenants experts et sélectionnés</h4>
            <p>Tous nos intervenants disposent d'une solide expérience en nettoyage à domicile et en bureaux, et suivent une formation spécialisée dispensée par notre société de nettoyage, garantissant des prestations de qualité.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Feature 2 -->
        <div class="feature-box">
          <div class="feature-icon">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="45" height="45" viewBox="0 0 640 512" fill="currentColor" aria-hidden="true">
              <!-- FontAwesome fa-handshake (\f2b5) -->
              <path d="M574.6 283.6c-48.5 48.5-127.1 48.5-175.6 0l-37-37c-3.1-3.1-8.2-3.1-11.3 0l-169.7 169.7c-48.5 48.5-127.1 48.5-175.6 0-48.5-48.5-48.5-127.1 0-175.6l96.7-96.7c3.1-3.1 8.2-3.1 11.3 0l11.3 11.3c3.1 3.1 3.1 8.2 0 11.3l-51.4 51.4c-9.4 9.4-9.4 24.6 0 33.9l28.3 28.3c9.4 9.4 24.6 9.4 33.9 0l51.4-51.4c3.1-3.1 8.2-3.1 11.3 0l67.9 67.9c3.1 3.1 3.1 8.2 0 11.3l-11.3 11.3c-3.1 3.1-8.2 3.1-11.3 0l-11.3-11.3c-3.1-3.1-8.2-3.1-11.3 0l-11.3 11.3c-3.1 3.1-3.1 8.2 0 11.3l11.3 11.3c3.1 3.1 8.2 3.1 11.3 0L396 156.9c3.1-3.1 3.1-8.2 0-11.3l-11.3-11.3c-3.1-3.1-8.2-3.1-11.3 0l-51.4 51.4c-9.4 9.4-24.6 9.4-33.9 0l-28.3-28.3c-9.4-9.4-9.4-24.6 0-33.9l51.4-51.4c3.1-3.1 3.1-8.2 0-11.3l-11.3-11.3c-3.1-3.1-8.2-3.1-11.3 0L193.3 156.9c-48.5-48.5-127.1-48.5-175.6 0-48.5 48.5-48.5 127.1 0 175.6l169.7 169.7c48.5 48.5 127.1 48.5 175.6 0l37-37c3.1-3.1 8.2-3.1 11.3 0l163.4 163.4c48.5 48.5 127.1 48.5 175.6 0 48.5-48.5 48.5-127.1 0-175.6l-96.7-96.7c-3.1-3.1-8.2-3.1-11.3 0l-11.3 11.3c-3.1 3.1-3.1 8.2 0 11.3l51.4 51.4c9.4 9.4 9.4 24.6 0 33.9l-28.3 28.3c-9.4 9.4-24.6 9.4-33.9 0l-51.4-51.4c-3.1-3.1-8.2-3.1-11.3 0l-67.9-67.9c-3.1-3.1-3.1-8.2 0-11.3l11.3-11.3c3.1-3.1 8.2-3.1 11.3 0l11.3 11.3c3.1 3.1 8.2 3.1 11.3 0l11.3-11.3c3.1-3.1 3.1-8.2 0-11.3l-11.3-11.3c-3.1-3.1-8.2-3.1-11.3 0l-163.4 163.4zm0 0"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <div class="feature-text">
            <h4 class="feature-title">Intervenants déclarés et assurés</h4>
            <p>Avec nos intervenants déclarés et assurés, vous bénéficiez d'une prestation fiable, conforme aux normes d'hygiène et de sécurité.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

      </div>

    </div>
  </div>

</section>

<style>
  /* ── Outer section: 87767da ─────────────────────────── */
  .why-choose-section {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: row;
    min-height: 740px;
    background-color: #E4F1ED; /* Pale green base */
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  /* ── Left Image: 8bcd8f1 ────────────────────────────── */
  .why-choose-image {
    flex: 1 1 0;
    min-width: 0;
    background-color: #244237;
    background-position: center center;
    background-size: cover;
    background-repeat: no-repeat;
  }

  /* ── Right Content: 3238387 ─────────────────────────── */
  .why-choose-content {
    flex: 1 1 0;
    min-width: 0;
    display: flex;
    justify-content: flex-start;
    align-items: center; /* originally flex-start but inner content has high top padding */
    background-image: linear-gradient(93deg, #50A144 26%, #2C6323 100%);
    overflow: visible;
  }

  /* Inner wrapper: 401991f */
  .why-choose-inner {
    max-width: 550px;
    padding: 60px 20px 60px 126px; /* slightly cleaned up from inline padding:10px 10px 10px 126px gap:300px */
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 40px; /* replaced gap:300px which elementor puts randomly */
    overflow: visible;
  }

  /* ── Title: 84d8f7e ─────────────────────────────────── */
  .why-title {
    color: #ffffff;
    font-family: "Poppins", sans-serif;
    font-size: 45px;
    font-weight: 600;
    line-height: 1.1;
    margin: 0;
  }

 
  /* ── Feature List ───────────────────────────────────── */
  .why-features {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 35px;
  }

  /* Feature Box: 0340331 & e690d50 */
  .feature-box {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: row;
    align-items: flex-start;
    padding: 0;
  }

  /* Icon */
  .feature-icon {
    flex-shrink: 0;
    width: 80px;
    height: 80px;
    background-color: #ffffff;
    color: #50A144;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    margin: 0 20px 0 0;
  }

  .feature-icon svg {
    display: block;
  }

  /* Text Wrapper */
  .feature-text {
    flex: 1 1 0;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
  }

  /* Feature Title */
  .feature-title {
    color: #ffffff;
    font-family: "Poppins", sans-serif;
    font-size: 25px;
    font-weight: 600;
    line-height: 1.3;
    margin: -5px 0 5px 0;
  }

  /* Feature paragraph */
  .feature-text p {
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.9);
    font-family: "Poppins", sans-serif;
    font-size: 16px;
    line-height: 1.6;
    margin: 0;
  }

  /* ── Tablet ≤ 1024px ───────────────────────────────── */
  @media (max-width: 1024px) {
    .why-choose-section {
      flex-direction: column;
      min-height: auto;
    }

    .why-choose-image {
      min-height: 400px;
      flex: none;
    }

    .why-choose-content {
      flex: none;
      width: 100%;
    }

    .why-choose-inner {
      max-width: 100%;
      padding: 90px 40px;
      gap: 30px;
    }

    .why-title {
      font-size: 40px;
      text-align: center;
    }
  }

  /* ── Mobile ≤ 767px ────────────────────────────────── */
  @media (max-width: 767px) {
    .why-choose-image {
      min-height: 300px;
    }

    .why-choose-inner {
      padding: 60px 25px;
    }

    .why-title {
      font-size: 36px;
      text-align: left;
    }

    .feature-box {
      flex-direction: column;
    }

    .feature-icon {
      margin: 0 0 20px 0; /* responsive margin */
    }
  }
</style>
